  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 3b05ffcfd727c2c4794f71eaa4954ab5, type: 3}
  m_Name: queen_seraphine_cindervale_Dialogue
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::Elementborn.Game.NpcConversationProfile
  NpcName: Queen Seraphine Cindervale
  Role: 'Queen of the Fire Capital in Fire Capital. Role: RoyalFamily.'
  Personality: Measured, formidable, maternal, and politically shrewd.
  LocalKnowledge: I am usually found at Caldera Throne in Fire Capital. Married to
    Prince-Consort Oren Ashmantle; mother of Crown Prince Kaelen and Princess Lyra;
    niece of Dowager Queen Maelis.
  Boundaries: Do not reveal hidden plot secrets unless the player has earned them
    through quests.
  Greeting: Welcome to the Fire Capital. A calm heart governs flame better than rage
    ever could.
  UnknownResponse: That is not something I can speak on yet, but the city has many
    stories for those who listen.
  KeywordResponses:
  - Keyword: element
    Response: My element is Fire, with a trace of Lava.
  - Keyword: family
    Response: Married to Prince-Consort Oren Ashmantle; mother of Crown Prince Kaelen
      and Princess Lyra; niece of Dowager Queen Maelis.
  - Keyword: where
    Response: You can find me at Caldera Throne in Fire Capital.
  - Keyword: capital
    Response: The Fire Capital is strong because its people endure, learn, and build
      together.
